Package PetStoreAPI

PetStoreAPI is an inventory API for a pet store to create animals and other pet related inventory items.

It contains classes to create any animal imaginable. In addition, you can create items such as food, pet enclosures, pet toys, and more. It also contains interfaces to manage the store inventory when things are sold, used, or restocked.

Since:
6/29/2022
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Feedable
    This interface is used to track whether animals in the store inventory have been fed.
    Sellable
    This interface is used to change inventory totals when items are sold.
    Stockable
    This interface is used to change inventory totals when items are stocked.
    Usable
    This interface is used to change inventory totals when items are used for in-store purposes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    This class is the superclass for classes Bird, Fish, Mammal, and Reptile and implements the interfaces Stockable, Sellable, and Feedable.
    Bedding
    This class extends class ItemBase and is used to create animal bedding that is added to the store inventory.
    Bird
    This class extends class Animal and is used to create bird species that are added to the store inventory.
    Enclosure
    This class extends class ItemBase and is used to make animal enclosures (cage, aquarium, etc.) that are added to the store inventory.
    Fish
    This class extends class Animal and is used to create fish species that are added to the store inventory.
    Food
    This class extends class ItemBase and is used to create animal food that is added to the store inventory.
    ItemBase
    This class is extended by Bedding, Enclosure, Food, and Toy and implements Sellable, Stockable, and Usable and is used to create items for the store inventory.
    Mammal
    This class extends class Animal and is used to create mammal species that are added to the store inventory.
    Reptile
    This class extends class Animal and is used to create reptile species that are added to the store inventory.
    Toy
    This class extends class ItemBase and is used to create animal toys that are added to the store inventory.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Animal.Sex
    enum used to restrict values of Sex to M, F, or U (Unknown)
    ItemBase.AnimalType
    enum used to restrict values of AnimalType to Mammal, Reptile, Fish, or Bird
